#zdep zshrc.d/modules,zshrc.d/options,zshrc.d/vars
### vim:ft=zsh:foldmethod=marker
###
### zsh misc. commands for interactive shells
###
### Frank Terbeck <ft@bewatermyfriend.org>
### Updated by:
### Lee Hinman <lee at writequit dot org>
